      "duration": 1.08,
      "size": 17280,
      "text": "这是一个挖不完洞的三角形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sierpinski-triangle",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/sierpinski-triangle/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.81,
      "size": 28944,
      "text": "取一个大三角，在正中间挖掉一个倒立的小三角。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sierpinski-triangle",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/sierpinski-triangle/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "剩下的三个角，各自又是一个三角形，继续挖下去。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sierpinski-triangle",
      "section_id": "recurse",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "recurse-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/sierpinski-triangle/xiaoxiao/recurse-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.77,
      "size": 28368,
      "text": "每一层都把每个三角分成四份，挖掉中间那份。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sierpinski-triangle",
      "section_id": "recurse",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "recurse-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/sierpinski-triangle/xiaoxiao/recurse-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.56,
      "size": 24912,
      "text": "第 n 层就留下三的 n 次方个小三角形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sierpinski-triangle",
      "section_id": "recurse",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "recurse-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/sierpinski-triangle/xiaoxiao/recurse-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "无限挖下去，图形的面积趋于零，边界却无限长。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sierpinski-triangle",
      "section_id": "selfsimilar",
      "line_id": "sim-1",
      "filename": "selfsimilar-sim-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/sierpinski-triangle/xiaoxiao/selfsimilar-sim-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.94,
      "size": 31104,
      "text": "把任意一个小角放大，你会看到和整体一模一样的结构。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sierpinski-triangle",
      "section_id": "selfsimilar",
      "line_id": "sim-2",
      "filename": "selfsimilar-sim-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/sierpinski-triangle/xiaoxiao/selfsimilar-sim-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.2,
      "size": 35136,
      "text": "这种局部与整体相似的性质，叫做自相似，是分形的灵魂。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sierpinski-triangle",
      "section_id": "selfsimilar",
      "line_id": "sim-3",
      "filename": "selfsimilar-sim-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/sierpinski-triangle/xiaoxiao/selfsimilar-sim-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "它的分形维数约为一点五八五，介于线与面之间。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sierpinski-triangle",
      "section_id": "chaos",
      "line_id": "cha-1",
      "filename": "chaos-cha-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/sierpinski-triangle/xiaoxiao/chaos-cha-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "换个玩法：随手点一个起点，随机选三角的一个顶点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sierpinski-triangle",
      "section_id": "chaos",
      "line_id": "cha-2",
      "filename": "chaos-cha-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/sierpinski-triangle/xiaoxiao/chaos-cha-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.07,
      "size": 33120,
      "text": "每次把当前点向选中的顶点移动一半，再重复几万次。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sierpinski-triangle",
      "section_id": "chaos",
      "line_id": "cha-3",
      "filename": "chaos-cha-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/sierpinski-triangle/xiaoxiao/chaos-cha-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.85,
      "size": 29664,
      "text": "神奇的是，这堆随机点竟然拼出了同一个三角形。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sierpinski-triangle",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
