      "duration": 1.72,
      "size": 27504,
      "text": "切换递归和混沌两种模式，看它们殊途同归。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "sierpinski-triangle",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/sierpinski-triangle/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "调整层数，层数越高，分形的细节就越丰富。"
